	        Send us your pictures   ·  Send us your stories THE Merchiston Senior Primary boys recently performed an outstanding rendition of what has taken place at Merchiston Preparatory school from 1892 to 2017 in the schools eisteddfod. Well done to all the boys and staff who sang, danced and performed. There may be some future stars among these boys.               - Supplied. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  